description: Alright. this is the eighth and last time I'm submitting a tab for Metropolis - Part I: "The Miracle and the Sleeper" I've been obsessed with this song for the longest time. And I wanted musicians to learn this song the right way. There has been a version on this website that wasn't that accurate to the studio. I tried many times to upload my new tab (but the sounds were always wrong, off-time parts, etc.) Now this will be my last submission of this song. Enjoy.
